Commentary Text: Boult to Ishan Kishan, out Caught by Samson!! Straight up off the top-edge and a simple catch to Samson. Ishan Kishan was living on the edge with his high-risk strategy tonight and this is a poor shot. Tight back of a length delivery on the hips, he is cramped on the pull and is in no position to get it away, predictably the top-edge goes up. Boult gets the breakthrough in the powerplay.
